divs: Sighting DetailsAfter I posted my report, I discovered the source of the Massive sound was a huge Gas Pipe Rupture not too far from my property. Details of the rupture can be found on WAFB channel 9 news. This is a big relief for me because I couldnt understand why this thing made so much noise and the characteristics of all the orbs that I normally see make absolutely zero noise.
